<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在之后的三个月里，毛克利没有离开村庄。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他忙着学习人类的生活方式和风俗习惯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先，他发现他必须一直穿着衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这太烦人了。”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他觉得上衣发痒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的鞋子夹住了他的脚趾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其次，他必须学会数钱，可他一点也不懂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么人类必须互相购买东西？”他问麦苏雅，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在森林里，你可以想拿什么就拿什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麦苏雅笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 这个问题很好。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也不知道该如何解释。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有，村里的孩子经常让他生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们一起玩儿游戏时，毛克利一个人站着看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女孩儿嘲笑他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“森林男孩儿什么游戏都不会玩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他也不会生火。”其中一个男孩儿说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他总是说错词。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利很生气，但他什么也没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每当他生气的时候，他就努力想起巴鲁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“森林法则说‘控制你的脾气’。”老熊教过他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在森林里，你的生活和食物都得靠这个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在这个村庄里，他的生活可能也靠这个。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天晚上，毛克利也和别人一样来到了无花果树下 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们见面讲故事，聊天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们坐在无花果树上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138394</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们也聊了几个小时。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138394</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当人们讲关于神、人和鬼魂的故事时，毛克利听着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥是村里的主要猎手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他讲了关于森林里所有野兽的长篇故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们听到黑豹、大象和野猪的故事时，眼睛睁得大大的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利忍不住捂住脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不想让任何人看到他嘲笑布尔迪奥的愚蠢故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可当布尔迪奥讲了一个又一个故事时，毛克利忍不住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他笑得肩膀发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥开始讲一个新的鬼故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个鬼住在森林老虎的身体里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是老虎偷了麦苏雅的儿子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”毛克利喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他再也无法安安静静地坐在那里了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“森林老虎不是鬼魂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他是真的。他的名字叫谢尔坎。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都转过头盯着毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥惊讶得一时说不出话来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他瞪着毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！森林小子在说话！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你这么聪明，为什么不去抓老虎？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的虎皮可是有奖的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“总有一天我会抓住他的。”毛克利小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猎人嘲笑着说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从现在起，当你的长辈说话时，你得闭嘴。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几分钟后，毛克利站了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我整晚都在听。”他大声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布尔迪奥只说了一两句真话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当毛克利离开时，布尔迪奥非常生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这孩子怎么敢这样让我难堪！”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会忘记这件事的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，村长拜访了麦苏雅和她的丈夫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说是时候给毛克利一份工作了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，毛克利和村里其他孩子们一起出去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从现在起，他将帮忙放村里的水牛和牛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>